														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4636978">
									

<p>Sorry for necro, but I feel the title insinuates that there is a risk being taken, and I don't think any 05 would be at risk visiting a random, safe scp. In my head, this is someone powerful outside of the Foundation, maybe even the president or something. Someone so popular that even simple agents recognize him and start stuttering in his presence.</p>
<p>I wonder if &quot;The guard stationed at the door started as he walked by, as if waking from a dream.&quot; was supposed to say stared instead of started.</p>
<p>edit: Found out that O5's aren't supposed to interact with ANY skips, so I guess that changes things&#8230;</p>

